<title>哈梅内伊遇害，普京发声</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5+%E5%93%88%E6%A2%85%E5%86%85%E4%BC%8A%E9%81%87%E5%AE%B3%EF%BC%8C%E6%99%AE%E4%BA%AC%E5%8F%91%E5%A3%B0</link>
